            <title>[THRIFT-5495] Go lib server not close client when shutdown</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-5495</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If there is client connection and no data is send&#65292;we will encounter hang druing server stop:&lt;br/&gt;
